00:38:14,617 --> 00:38:15,883
Hello!

482
00:38:16,954 --> 00:38:17,954
Ms. Hawkins.

483
00:38:19,302 --> 00:38:21,298
That girl yesterday,

484
00:38:21,885 --> 00:38:23,418
