00:39:05,887 --> 00:39:07,341
tall tales, not to believe you.

498
00:39:07,366 --> 00:39:09,095
But they weren't made up, were they?

499
00:39:09,935 --> 00:39:11,501
They were true.

500
00:39:13,392 --> 00:39:14,725
