503
00:39:19,784 --> 00:39:21,684
What are you so afraid of
all of a sudden?

504
00:39:22,406 --> 00:39:24,473
She do that to you?

505
00:39:27,824 --> 00:39:30,554
In their natural state in the water,

506
00:39:31,067 --> 00:39:32,676
