509
00:39:39,385 --> 00:39:41,385
It caused a lot of misery.

510
00:39:42,145 --> 00:39:43,711
What do you mean?

511
00:39:43,964 --> 00:39:45,754
Your family's history in this town

512
00:39:45,786 --> 00:39:47,753
